{"lemma":"غُسْلُ","slug":"غُسْلُ","root":"غ.س.ل","root_slug":"غ-س-ل","root_link":"/words/roots/غ-س-ل","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":4,"pos_tags":["noun","verb"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":7},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["","n31849","n31850","n31851","n31853","n31854"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%BA%D9%8F%D8%B3%D9%92%D9%84%D9%8F"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to clean by washing, to wash","tags":["transitive"],"examples":[{"text":"لَا تَنْسَى غَسْل الْأَطْبَاق بَعْد تَنَاوُل وَجْبَتِك.","english":"Don't forget to wash the dishes after your meal."}]},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to remove by washing, to wash off","tags":["transitive"]},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to wash up","tags":["transitive"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of غَسَلَ (ḡasala) (form I)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb","transitive"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of غَسَلَ (ḡasala) (form I)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb","transitive"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"irregular verbal noun of اِغْتَسَلَ (iḡtasala) (form VIII)","tags":["form-of","irregular","noun-from-verb","transitive"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"ghusl","tags":["transitive"]}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":["/ɣa.sa.la/","/ɣas.sa.la/","/ɣasl/","/ɣusl/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n31849","headword_ar":"غَسْلٌ","root":"gsl","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"inf. n. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gasalahu","text_ar":"غَسَلَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S, MA, Mgh, O, Msb, K:) or, accord. to some, this and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gusolN","text_ar":"غُسْلٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"have one and the same meaning; and the saying that this is the case is ascribed to Sb: (Msb:) or, as some say, the latter is the inf. n., and the former is the subst. (MF, TA.) See also the next paragraph."}],"source_refs":["S","MA","Mgh","O","Msb","K"]},{"entry_id":"n31850","headword_ar":"غُسْلٌ","root":"gsl","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"the subst. from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gasalahu","text_ar":"غَسَلَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e. a subst. signifying"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A washing"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (S, Msb:) or a subst. (IKoot, Mgh, Msb, K, TA) from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlAgtsAl","text_ar":"الاغتسال"},{"kind":"text","text":", (IKoot, Mgh, Msb, TA,) and [as such] signifying"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a complete washing"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of oneself,"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e.]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the whole person:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(IKoot, T, Mgh, Msb, TA:) it is in consequence of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"janaAbap","text_ar":"جَنَابَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"[q. v.], and of childbirth, and for [the prayers of] Friday, and is the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"washing"},{"kind":"text","text":"of the dead; but in other cases, the word ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gasolN","text_ar":"غَسْلٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", with fet-h, is used: (Ham p. 30:) and one says ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gusulN","text_ar":"غُسُلٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"as well as"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gusolN","text_ar":"غُسْلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, O,) the former being a dial. var. of the latter: (TA:) El-Kumeyt says, describing a wild ass,"},{"kind":"quote","text":"taHota AlA^alaA='api fiY nawoEayoni mino gusulK\n                      \n                     \n                        baAtaA Ealayohi bitasojaAlK wataqoTaAri"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Beneath the"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tree called)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^alaA='ap","text_ar":"اَلَا=ءَة"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in two sorts of washing that continued during the night upon him with much pouring and much dropping"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; meaning that the water that was upon the tree poured upon him at one time; and at one time, that of the rain: (S, TA:) the pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gusolN","text_ar":"غُسْلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^agosaAlN","text_ar":"اَغْسَالٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Msb.) See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gasolN","text_ar":"غَسْلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". ―         -b2-  And see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gasuwlN","text_ar":"غَسُولٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":["S","Msb","IKoot","Mgh","K","TA","T","O"]},{"entry_id":"n31851","headword_ar":"غِسْلٌ","root":"gsl","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A preparation for washing the head, consisting of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xiTomiY~","text_ar":"خِطْمِىّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"marsh-mallows"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and other things"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Mgh, O, Msb, K)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of a similar kind,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh, Msb, K,) ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with water,"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"as"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"leaves of"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"species of lote-tree called"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sidor","text_ar":"سِدْر"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Msb,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Tiyn","text_ar":"طِين"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Tiynapu Alr~aA^osi","text_ar":"طِينَةُ الرَّاْسِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", [meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fullers' earth,"},{"kind":"text","text":"which is often used in the bath and elsewhere instead of soap,] (Mgh,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^u$onaAn","text_ar":"اُشْنَان"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"potash"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (TA:) [and app."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"any wash for the head:"},{"kind":"text","text":"] and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gisolapN","text_ar":"غِسْلَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies the same: (Mgh, K:) and also (this latter)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"leaves of the myrtle:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"perfume;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TiybN","text_ar":"طِيبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"what a woman puts into her hair on the occasion of combing and dressing it:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gisolapN muTar~aApN","text_ar":"غِسْلَةٌ مُطَرَّاةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"being"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"myrtle"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"-leaves"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"rendered fragrant with aromatic perfumes, used in combing and dressing one's hair:"},{"kind":"text","text":"one should not say"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gasolapN","text_ar":"غَسْلَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S, O.) IAar cites the following verse (S, O) of 'Abd-Er-Rahmán Ibn-Dárah El-Ghatafánee, (O,)"},{"kind":"quote","text":"fayaA layola A_in~a Algisola maA dumoti A^ay~imFA\n                      \n                     \n                        EalaY~a HaraAmN laA yamas~uniYa Algisolu"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"And, O Leylà,"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"layola","text_ar":"لَيْلَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"being a contraction of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"layolaY","text_ar":"لَيْلَى"},{"kind":"text","text":", but in the O it is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yA jumolu","text_ar":"يا جُمْلُ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"O Juml,"},{"kind":"text","text":")"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"verily the wash for the head, as long as thou remainest husbandless, shall be unlawful to me: the wash for the head shall not touch me"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: i. e. I will not need the wash for the head by my"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jimaAE","text_ar":"جِمَاع"},{"kind":"text","text":"of other than her: [he says thus] in eager desire of taking her in marriage. (S, O.) ―         -b2-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gasuwlN","text_ar":"غَسُولٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".       -A2-  And see also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gusalapN","text_ar":"غُسَلَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":["S","Mgh","O","Msb","K","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n31853","headword_ar":"غُسَلٌ","root":"gsl","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gusalapN","text_ar":"غُسَلَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n31854","headword_ar":"غُسُلٌ","root":"gsl","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gusolN","text_ar":"غُسْلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":[]}]}}